casebody.data:
No. 233,

Mise.

Kilpatrick v. Texas & Pacific Railway Co. William H. DeParcq, Gerald F. Finley and Arnold B. Elkind for petitioner. Theodore Kiendl, William H. Timbers and Cleveland C. Cory for respondent.

This case is assigned for hearing on the motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus or certio-rari.
